caption:
🗣️Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang: “My time at Barça was the best six months of my career. I’ve never enjoyed playing football and going to training so much. I even went to train with the team on off-days. That should tell you. It was incredible”

He gave everything for the badge. He arrived on a free transfer, scored in El Clásico, delivered when it mattered, and left with class — like a true professional. 👏🏻 

🇬🇦 Aubameyang for Barcelona: 
🏟️ Games: 24 
🚀 Goals: 13 
🎯 Assists: 1
